description: This API accepts a batch of files, and optionally tags, to create images. There is a limit of 64 images and 20 tags.

batch.description: The batch of image files to add. Limited to 64 images and 20 tags per batch.

isbatchsuccessful.description: True if all of the images in the batch were created successfully, otherwise false.

images.description: List of the image creation results.
